reviews.review_text: Baltimore 82' This is a really nice 82' show with a great set list and fine playing.Seems like their having fun.

Noodles TLEO is a perfect example of early 80’s Jerry guitar. Sure his vocals are close to shot (only to return in the late 80’s) but damn is Tiger hot! Fast and clean. Weaving in and out as he climbs the ladder to enlightenment and cosmic devotion
Inspiration move me brightly Definitely worth a listen or two!
